title: Status Quo - Live: The Frantic Four Reunion 2013 / 2CD
description:
A newly compiled and re-mastered double CD recorded live at Hammersmith, 
with audio taken from across the two shows on the 15th/16th March 2013.

Status Quo 

The Frantic Four Reunion 2013

Live at Hammersmith 

2CDs / 2013 / Remastered / VBR-V0

Tracklist:

CD 1:

01. Intro/Junior's Wailing 4.21

02. Backwater 4.20

03. Just Take Me 4.56

04. Is There A Better Way 3.47

05. In My Chair 3.13

06. Blue Eyed Lady 3.47

07. Little Lady 3.14

08. Most Of The Time 3.19

09. (April) Spring, Summer And Wednesdays 4.13

10. Railroad 5.51

11. Oh Baby 4.49

CD 2:

01 - 12. 4500 Times 5.13

02 - 13. Rain 5.04

03 - 14. Big Fat Mama 5.27

04 - 15. Down Down 5.57

05 - 16. Roadhouse Blues 6.48

06 - 17. Don't Waste My Time 4.27

07 - 18. Bye Bye Johnny 6.

"The band hit every song home just like in that other kind of dream, the one where you do everything right." - Classic Rock 

"It sounded fantastic. And they, like us, were clearly getting a tremendous kick out of revisiting these long-neglected songs." - The Times

:)
